---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Hearing Center Book Catalog">
  <article class="about">
    <h1>About This Catalog</h1>

    <p class="lede">
      This catalog is a labor of love — a curated list of books featuring Deaf,
      Hard of Hearing, and DeafBlind characters, built by volunteers affiliated
      with the Friends of the Hearing Center at UPMC Children's Hospital of
      Pittsburgh.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h2>Our mission</h2>
      <p>
        Every child deserves to see themselves reflected in the stories they read.
        We maintain this collection so that families, librarians, educators, and
        young readers can easily find books that celebrate Deaf, Hard of Hearing,
        and DeafBlind experiences.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>The volunteers</h2>
      <p>
        This list has been researched, reviewed, and compiled by a dedicated
        group of volunteers — parents, audiologists, educators, and members of
        the Deaf and Hard of Hearing community.
      </p>
      <p class="placeholder">
        <em>(Placeholder — send us the list of volunteers you'd like named here
        and any photos or bios, and we'll add them.)</em>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Suggest a book or report an error</h2>
      <p>
        Know of a book we're missing? Spotted an error in an entry? We'd love to
        hear from you.
      </p>
      <p class="placeholder">
        <em>(Placeholder — send us the email address or submission form link
        you'd like to use for book suggestions and corrections.)</em>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>About Friends of the Hearing Center</h2>
      <p>
        Friends of the Hearing Center is a nonprofit supporting the UPMC
        Children's Hospital of Pittsburgh Hearing Center and the families it
        serves.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem 0 3rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-ink-light);
    margin: 0 0 2.25rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0 0 0.65rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-ink-light);
    margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
  }

  .placeholder {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    background: var(--color-accent-soft);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
  }
</style>
